ride up to here, but things are quieter now. I would say it's close to equal})
(9... e5 {is the alternative} 10. Bc4 Be7 11. Bd2 O-O 12. Nc3 d6 13. Nd5 Be6
14. Be3 Bg5 {with a position that resembles the Sveshnikov variation. White is
