{Black to play} 15... Ne5 $1 {I recommend this move order. The most important
thing to remember here is why not the natural 15...Qb8? This move allows 16.
Nb3 and although is not fatal, remember that now 16...Bd8 17.Bf4 Ne5 18.Bxe5
dxe5.is not of everyone's taste. I would avoid this structure.} 16. Na4 Nfd7 {
See Ganguly,S-Arencibia,W Torino 2006} *

