{White has just played c4. What's black's best idea here?} 10... b6 $1 {
/\ Bc5 with the idea of Bc5 next. Otherwise, black is simply cramped in a
hedgehog without much counterplay. If you search in the database, you will
find white has done very well with this move. It seems that the right plan for
black is to fight for the center with the move} 11. Nc3 (11. Qh5 $5 {can be
